id: pm-q4jp
title: Sentry CLI token needs broader scopes for issue analysis
description: "Current sentry-cli auth token only has org:ci scope (sufficient for source map uploads). Needs project:read and event:read scopes to query issues programmatically for automated error analysis. The Sentry MCP plugin also requires authentication. Should create a separate read-only token for analytics."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
