close_reason: Sentry CLI successfully queried 5 issues using SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN with personal admin token. Token scopes are sufficient for issue list/analysis. Full analysis report created at scripts/prod/telemetry/reports/2026-05-02-sentry-analysis.md.
